\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\sl262\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf6 In the seclusion of a small private storage room, Sarah takes a moment to prepare Evan for the impending fundraiser. With a mix of excitement and concern, she instructs him to mind his P\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s and Q\u8217\'92s, particularly around her boss, Marcus Chamberlain, who bears a striking resemblance to Morgan Freeman. Her guidance is filled with both faith in Evan\u8217\'92s abilities and anxiety about how the evening will unfold, setting the stage for what promises to be an unforgettable event.<!$Scr_Ps::4><$Scr_Ps::3>}
